Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:52.86,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.70,Default,Yin,0000,0000,0000,,Đừng bỏ tôi!
